title: Concert Series starts at Vanderbilt Presbyterian
text:
Concert Series starts again at Vanderbilt Presbyterian Church of Naples VPCNAPLES 3:54 PM, Oct 7, 2015 
Come to Vanderbilt Presbyterian Church and enjoy a beautiful concert on selected Sundays. Doors open 45 minutes before performance time, seating is first-come, first-served. Nursery care provided, free-will offering appreciated. 
First concert will be on Sunday, October 11, 4:00 pm. 
We are honored to present "The Chrysalis Chamber Players". This is a non-profit chamber ensemble dedicated to presenting exciting new programs to south Florida. This program features co-founders trumpeter Mary Elizabeth Bowden and pianist Catherine Lan, and guest violin soloist Anne Chicheportiche in a program with strings. Featuring James MacMillan's vibrant "Seraph" for Trumpet and Strings and works by Chopin, Albinoni, and Saint-SaÃ«ns.
